OL,3,CSearch underway for two miniature
OL,4,Chorses stolen from a farm in Kent
OL,6,FTwo rare miniature horses have been
OL,7,Fstolen from a farm near Edenbridge in
OL,8,FKent.
OL,10,FPolice say a gate was damaged at the
OL,11,Fproperty on Marsh Green Road between
OL,12,F8pm on 27 May and 1am on 28 May.
OL,14,FThe horses are a breeding pair of the
OL,15,FArgentine Falabella and are both just
OL,16,F2ft 8in tall.
OL,18,FThe stallion is described as white
OL,19,Fwith brown spots, and the mare is
OL,20,Fdescribed as black.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/2
