OL,4,Chorses stolen from a farm in Kent
OL,6,FInvestigators are urging people in the
OL,7,Flocal area to check CCTV and dashcam
OL,8,Ffootage while calling upon any
OL,9,Fwitnesses to get in contact with Kent
OL,10,FPolice.
